headline.main: Air War Is Waged Night and Day Over the Central Front in Russia; Correspondent Undergoes Bombing Attack -- Hears Captured German Airmen Call Soviet Conflict a 'Great Surprise'

lead_paragraph: WITH THE RED ARMY, on the Central Front, Sept 22 (Delayed) -- Three parachutists are swinging down against the setting sun as the last plane taxies to rest and the ground crew covers it with pine boughs. These are only practice leaps, the officer explains.
abstract: int with German flier prisoners and air war on Central Front described
